Class SBMLLoad

  • java.lang.Object
    • project.SBMLLoad

  • public class SBMLLoad
extends java.lang.Object

      • loadSBML

        public void loadSBML(java.lang.String path)
              throws javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamException,
                     java.io.IOException
        loadSBML() load the Model, the number of Reactions/Species, the lower/upper bounds and the objective coefficients from the provided SBML document.

        The method sets also the objective function.

        Parameters:
        path - the hole path of the SBML document
        Throws:
        javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamException
        java.io.IOException
